根据write(2), write返回正数时可能只是已经把部分buf写入文件。
可参考以下代码来尽量把全部数据写入文件：

```
static ssize_t isulad_save_log(int fd, const void *buf, size_t count)
{
    ssize_t nret = 0;
    size_t  nwritten;

    for (nwritten = 0; nwritten < count;) {
        nret = write(fd, buf + nwritten, count - nwritten);
        if (nret < 0） {
            if (errno == EINTR || errno == EAGAIN || errno == EWOULDBLOCK) {
                continue;
            } else {
                return nret; // hard to go on writing
            }
        } else {
            nwritten += nret;
        }
    }
    return count;
}
```

