## 根因分析
image_store_big_data_size函数请求读锁
```
    if (!image_store_lock(SHARED)) {
        ERROR("Failed to lock image store with shared lock, not allowed to get image big data size assignments");
        return -1;
    }
```
在未释放锁的情况下，其调用函数get_size_with_update_big_data，该函数调用的image_store_set_big_data中请求写锁，从而出现死锁
```
    if (!image_store_lock(EXCLUSIVE)) {
        ERROR("Failed to lock image store with exclusive lock, not allowed to change image big data assignments");
        ret = -1;
        goto out;
    }
```
## 解决办法
>在image_store_big_data_size函数中及时将请求的锁释放

>MR: https://gitee.com/openeuler/iSulad/commit/20b179c56fb4227d780336205d07f6be7383b984

